content.detailedDescription:
This was years ago, i was still in high school. i was up late one night surfing the web. we lived in a ranch home a mile or so from a small lake that channeled into lake michigan. we lived off of a small residential road, our home was surrounded by sandy fields and patches of forest. 
anyways, our garage door was open and my mother's car was parked in the driveway. from the computer chair (as i turned around) i noticed that my mom's car lights were left on. the garage door being open made this visible. the car was parked perhaps, 30 or so feet from the garage building. note: our house had an attached garage. 

noticing this, i decided to go outside and turn of her headlights. i can't remember turning the headlights off (even though i must have). however, i do remember (either before of after turning the headlights off) seeing a saucer like object about 150 feet away from me. it was hovering about 10-20 feet off the ground and lights were emitted from the entire circumference beneath it. the size is hard to describe, i would say that it's circumference was 200-300 feet. i could compare the size to that of a reservoir of a smaller water tower. it's hard to think of something to compare it's size to. 

i was absolutely terrified. i felt like i was frozen with fear, but i somehow managed to make it back to my house? for the life of me, i cannot remember why i didn't attempt to wake my mom or brother up, or why i didn't go back outside to see if it was still there. also, it is hard for me to recall what happened afterwards. i can't remember if i went to my bed and fell asleep, or if i was awake all night terrified. i don't think i spoke of this event for months. i was sort of in denial at first that it even happened. it's weird, and i just don't know what to think of it.
content.summary: Saucer like object, just as they appear in movies and television. emitting light from circumference

content.detailedDescription: My father was walking to the grocery store right down the street. he noticed a long bright light up on the mountain ridge to the west. he came in and got me and his girlfriend and we went out in the front yard to watch this strange light. it was there for a good 30 minutes or more, and for three nights we saw this. the unidentified objects most mysterious thing was that it would be a small white light and then all of a sudden get brighter and brighter to where it was blinding and we could hardly look at it. it would move up and down a little but mostly kept its path going slowly back and forth in a north and south direction. it would blink, change color to red, disappear then reappear. a few times it changed from one object into two than back as one again. i have many short video recordings on my camera. every time i try to submit them it knocks me offline. this is my forth attempt at submitting this so i am just going to attach one video and one picture. you can let me know if you would like to see the rest. to see everything this ufo was doing you would have to watch all the videos. what is going on in bullhead city ?? my father and i are very interested in finding out what that was we were watching for three days.

content.detailedDescription:
I went to my usual spot outside across from where i work for my smoke break  when i was surprised again to see 3 lights going around and around in the distance.  the lights were not that high in the sky, but, some distance above the treetops and always stayed in the clouds so that no shape could be seen.  (again they reminded me of a flashlight beam) i stood there watching them as they went in a counterclockwise direction.  the circle direction was not uniform and whenever the third light went around it didn't go all the way to the left, but, dropped down and all 3 of the lights kind of grouped together, then one of them would go towards the right and they would keep continuing this somewhat circular pattern.  i saw a plane around 6:25 pm coming from the east to west direction and the plane was up real high.  the lights would have been very far down below them and to their right if they were able to see that low.
since i had noticed 3 lights going around just a few weeks ago, i have been looking out to see if they would come back.  this time i watched the lights from a distance and the last time they were more overhead.  the circular pattern continued, but, the way they circled around was different.
when i left the area to return back to work, i stopped a couple of times to look back and noticed one of the lights went a bit higher up in the sky when i walked up the road and then went in the building.
content.summary: 3 unknown lights going around in a sort of counterclockwise circle

content.summary: Bright green, then turned orange light, then turned into6 lights in arow horizontally, then went vertical

content.detailedDescription: Eran las cinco treinta de la tarde, estaba pintando una estructura metalica que esta en la platabanda de mi casa.Cuando mire hacia el norte como a 70 a 75 grados sobre el orizonte, vi el ovni volando, pense que era un avion pero al observar que carecia de planos y cola, crei que era un misil, y cinceramente que va a hacer un misil en venezuela? imposible!. trate de verlo en detalle era gris claro con una llama o especie de llama muy corta, parecia mas bien electricidad pues no salia humo ni nada,emitia una luz palpitante que no alcance a ver de que punto exacto del ovni provenia,pero parecia provenir de la cola, en la parte de adelante se notava un cierto brillo metalico leve,se movio en linea recta, el evento duro pocos segundos y simplemente desaparecio en el cielo.Simplemente me causo asombro, pues toda mi vida he trabajo en la aviacion y se como es y se ve un avion, y esto no era un avion.
content.summary: El ovni tenia forma de cigarro el doble de grande que un avion de pasajeros,era de color gris claro ,luz en la cola como una llama azul y un destello azul palpitante.

content.detailedDescription: My brother and i were driving north on route 24. we were passing the taunton mall exit and in the distance i spotted a single bright light hovering over the highway but it was toward the northwest part of the sky. we were joking that is was a ufo. as we kept driving and getting closer i noticed it hasn't moved at all like a plane or helicopter would, it was hovering and pulsating.  as soon as i said to my brother that it was definitely not a plane,  we both saw another bright light exactly the same appear out of nowhere.  this light was hovering and pulsating directly in the north part of the sky.There was a good distance between the two lights. we were completely amazed at what we were seeing.  a few seconds after the second light appeared,the first light completely dissapeared.  it never moved at all. it looked like it just turned it's lights off and was gone. as we continued to get closer i was trying to get a good look at the second light but i lost it over the tree line, right before the route 44 exit in raynham, ma off of route 24. this was the only sighting i've ever seen and i'm hoping it won't be the last.
content.summary: Observed a single light hovering over rte. 24. then another appeared out of nowhere. as the second one appeared the first dissapeared. just vanished, lost sight of second light while driving. they were hovering and was not a plane or helicopter.

We seen multiple objects (approximately 15-25) moving very erratically across the sky ( almost like shooting stars). the objects appeared to be sphere/orb like and formed clusters which they constantly broke apart from. i first thought that they were shooting stars but there was too many and the objects jumped all over the sky and it was daylight. my son also saw the objects... he has been working on a small scale radar for a school project that was able to receive multiple hits in the approximate location of the objects. i recorded the objects with my phone. the objects were barely visible in the recording but the recording of our voices was cut off and a very strange sound was heard. my son also captured a picture where the objects were visible by some degree especially after enhancement.  


the audio is from the video which is too large to attach, one picture is original where you can barley see the orbs, and the other is enhanced where you can see the orbs well... only 2 of the orbs were captured in the pictures.

i am very frightened about the sound after reviewing the video.

content.detailedDescription:
I was taking a late night walk on the beach at tybee island.  i lived there for around 5 years.  i walked down the main (public) part of the beach and then around the island onto some private properties, with private beach fronts.  i used to go there sometimes in the middle of the night and sit in the grass under a few large trees, thinking about things and enjoying the serenity of the ocean at night.  i know i was probably trespassing, but it was a private part of the beach and i liked to relax at night on the beach without the occasional person or flashlight of a vacationing late night beach goers.

while laying in the grass on a lot elevated a bit above the shoreline, i noticed movement in the sky and saw a cigar shaped craft about maybe 1000-2000 feet in the air, about 1-3 miles away, flying towards the shore, but off in the distance.   it made no noise and was a dull silver color, cigar shaped, maybe 20-40 feet in height and about 100 feet long.  since it was dark and only the moonlight was providing light, i could not make out any details of this craft, only that it was cigar shaped and obviously under intelligent control.  when it got about a quarter mile away, the craft simply vanished.  i was scared because i observed this craft flying in this flight path for about 2 minutes.  then, it was gone. my heart raced.  

as i was trying to process what had just happened, maybe 30 seconds to a minute later, i again saw movement in the sky and about 1-3 miles away, flying in about the same flight path, although slightly descending and ascending while on this path and moving a little from side to side.  descending and ascending maybe a few hundred feet and moving maybe 100 feet from side to side.  definitely not a completely straight flight path.  again, after the object had flown this flight path over the ocean and was about a quarter mile from the shore, it again vanished, only to appear about a minute later miles away, again flying a flight path similar to the last.  wether this was the same craft or multiple craft is unknown.  they looked exactly the same, from what i could see in the dark, at 2am.

i wanted this happen at least 10-15 times, over the course of 30-45 minutes.  then, the craft vanished as it had done before and never reappeared.  i wanted about 10 minutes for it to reappear and it didn't.  i left the beach and never returned to that private area of the beach, although i did live on the island for another 2 years, visiting other areas of the public beach often.  i had no other sightings during the time i lived there.
content.summary: Cigar shaped craft observed flying high above the ocean, not far from beach

content.detailedDescription: at 7:03 pm i witnessed a fireball straight west of my location (my back yard)that i thought was a meteor coming straight down in the sky at extremely high rate of speed; that is until it started slowing down and it changed from bright orange fireball with a trail behind it, to a flashing red light and made a complete u-turn in the shape of a j at break neck speed and shot straight back up into the sky and disappeared quickly after changing directions.The whole event took place in a very brief amount of time. maybe 10-15 seconds tops. i was unable to get my phone out in time to film it because when i realized it wasn't a shooting star as i first thought, it only was visible for a couple of seconds before disappearing. shortly after what i witnessed, i heard the rumble of a helicopter very low to the ground. it was very loud and shook the house. i was able to get my phone out and started recording. i could not find where the noise was coming from until i walked around the side of the house and witnessed a blacked out helicopter with no lights on traveling in the direction of the ufo. the other helicopter was traveling away from the direction and had it's lights on. there was also another helicopter flying in from the south quite a ways away of which i could hear as well but the sound was much more faint. i was not able to pick up the black helicopter that i saw with my naked eye on my phone but you can clearly hear the audio.
content.summary: Ufo that looked like meteor at first

content.detailedDescription:
It was too around 4:30am on sunday, early morning of nov 8th, 2015. my husband and i were coming home from our date and parked on the street, needing to walk roughly 100ft to reach my home ( i live on a dead end street in san gabriel, ca).
 i was facing east waiting for my husband to calmly finish his cigarette (while i was freezing by the way) and noticed a bright light coming straight from the southeast, which at first i thought was a regular airplane or helicopter, but noticed it was a bit unusually brighter than that. i then thought it could be a satellite? i then asked my husband to look.
id say it was about 3-4 miles away distance on ground and air when it startes hovering in place and my husband and i stared at each other questioning what the hell we were seeing? a man controlled drone people use to record maybe? 
anyway i began to feel very uneasy, as i could not figure out what it was and it was still dark like night time. i told him  i had seen plenty and insisted we go inside.
i grabbed his arm and kept gently tugging on him to start walking so we begin walking and the thing starts looking like it's moving towards us as well. and we both stopper again in the middle of the street ardendale at the dead end and it stops now about 2 miles distance ground maybe e miles high in the air hovering in place this time i could see clearer that this thing had 3 circular blinking lights in a sequential motio  left to right. thats when i pulled out my phone to record it real fast since i had to go inside since my mom babysat my son. (again i thought back to thinking may be this is a chopper? but it was way to big and helicopters pass by everyday with blue and red or white lights. )
after the video my husband asked "what is that"? we make our way through the long driveway walking northbound and the thing slowly starts moving from its direction in the se to north very slowly hovering then continuing n so on . then i went inside very nervous woke up my mom and freaked out.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: 3 blinking lights, felt like my husband and i were being messed with as it would stop and go as we would stop and go to look at it .

content.detailedDescription:
Home watching tv then my husband called, he had just left home.
my husband called telling me to go outside to look that there were two orange red glowing orbs out in front of him in the sky headed towards our house.
i had no idea, never seen anything like it.
i saw only one orb, my husband said that he saw the second one head towards the ground in a wooded area, he lost sight. i saw one orb pulsating orange/red just as it reached my neighbors yard. i could see over the top of my garage. it was still. pulsating. i took a picture with my phone and the flash went off & then the object moved forward then turned maybe 15 degrees, went over our other garage across our field into a wooded area just above the tree line and disappeared.
i had a lot of anxiety. i wasn't afraid, that was strange for me, i think. disbelief. trying to understand what i saw.
i lost sight when it just disappeared.

content.detailedDescription: While waiting at traffic light, we noticed a very bright light in night sky.It was moving towards us. because of unusual brightness i observed it as it flew over head. i was below it as it passed by, light was very intense, could not look directly at it. no sound that i could hear coming from it. i noticed at rear was five straight lines coming from it, they were about 30 percent the length of main body. each one had two flashing lights on them. about mid way was a white flashing light, and at the end was a flashing green light. this was on each of the five pieces coming from rear. speed was not at all fast, about average speed of a small air plane. only several hundred feet high. i did not remember seeing this sort of light in the sky before. it may have been some one using a radio controled drone was my first thought. becuase of the light being so bright, i thought perhaps not. i was not able to see it disappear as traffic light turned to green, and i had to drive on.
content.summary: Very bright white light aiming down,  five finger like projections from rear, white flashing light on center, green flashing light at ends of each

content.detailedDescription:
1. jeg er hjemme og får en telefon fra min venn som bor noen mil fra mysen. han har nettopp fått tatt noen bra bilder av ufoen som har kommet tilbake jevnlig i 4 uker. etter jeg ser hans fasinerande bilder.. bestemmer jeg meg for å ta bilde av den store lys stjernen som står utenfor meg. da jeg ser på bildene ser jeg at dette lysfenomenet er i bevegelse.
den forsvant fra mitt øye rundt 9 tiden da det var lyst.
dette er mitt andre møte med objektet. 

første gang var 9. oktober rundt 06.30 da var det tre lys objekter mye nærmere 
oss (101-501 ft). de står sidelengs plassert fra hverandre. den fremste var stor og tydelig, føltes som jeg connected med den/det, føltes bra. fram til jeg satte meg i taxi.

andre gang var 17. oktober fra balkongen hjemme, rundt samme klokkeslett.
de var fortsatt tre objekter skrått plassert på himmelen. bare litt lengre unna denne gangen. de var utenfor her mens solen sto opp og forsvant ikke fra mitt syn før dagen var for lys.

tredje gang var i går 11.11.15 da var det bare en og ennå litt lengre vekk.

på 2 og 3 møte skjer samme bakgrunns aktivitet på himmelen. (begge dagene var det mørke gråe skyer i bakgrunnen av disse.) der ser jeg blinkende lys som hvit/gul og grønne lys blinke seg igjennom disse lange grå skyene i en veldig stor hastighet.
content.summary: Dette er tredje gangen dette blinkende lys fenomene er i nærheten av mitt åsted. samme klokke slett som de andre gangene.

content.detailedDescription: I was leaving home with my mother around 8:30 am when i see a plane pass by on final approach to the airport, when i looked up i see a bright, shine  metallic kind of object and i asked myself what could that be, i started looking at it and i realize that's neither a star nor a plane so kept looking, my mother was in the car and i said to her "mom get out of the car and look at this" but by the time she is out of the car the object had disappear. at that moment the sighting only lasted a few secs so we got in the car and left. when we get back to the house a little after 11 am i look up again and there it is only this time my mother goes back into the house and get the binoculars. i looked up and i finally see the object triangular with three white glowing lights under and then changing shape and position but still static, however in my mothers opinion it looks like a cilinder, she at some point sees a red light. we kept looking at the object and for the next hour and 10 mint but during that time my father comes  and also witness the event. after sometime we lost sight of the object because it got cloudy but it moved and saw it again for like 10 more min. the clouds rolled in again just to lose sight of but at the end a saw it one last time but with big difference that this time there were two instead of one just to disappear between the clouds. to be honest i don't know what to think of it but it was really impressive since is the first time something like that happens to me.
content.summary: Couldn't describe its something i've never see in my life
